data.description: COUNTRY LIVING at it's finest!!  Almost 5 acres with unobstructed views!!  A beautiful, practically new home with an open floorplan, tall ceilings, ceiling fans in every room, lots of natural light AND an enclosed 480sf deck.  Bring your livestock, RV, plenty of room for anything you own!! Kitchen is spacious with deep drawers, plenty of cabinets and counter space, island with a sink and surface you can put hot pans on, large pantry.  Master bath has a wonderful, deep garden tub, double sinks, beautiful walk in shower.  The living room, dining room, kitchen and bathrooms were all painted this year.  The green house will be finished by close of escrow.  There's a horse shoe pit and fire pit in the back yard with solar lights.  Solar lights all around the house also!!
